<!-- Definition and symptoms -->
'''死產'''，或稱為胎死腹中，通常定義是在[[懷孕|懷孕]]之後的胎兒死亡<ref name="NIH2014Def">{{cite web|title=Stillbirth: Overview|url=https://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/stillbirth/Pages/default.aspx|accessdate=4 October 2016|date=23 September 2014|publisher=NICHD|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161005085055/https://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/stillbirth/Pages/default.aspx|archivedate=2016-10-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。描述胎兒在母體子宮內即死亡的現象<ref name="WHO2016">{{Cite web|title=Stillbirths|url=http://www.who.int/maternal_child_adolescent/epidemiology/stillbirth/en/|accessdate=2016-09-29|publisher=World Health Organization|language=en-GB|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161002035346/http://www.who.int/maternal_child_adolescent/epidemiology/stillbirth/en/|archivedate=2016-10-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>。死產可能導致母親[[內疚|內疚]]。死產和[[流產|流產]]不同，流產是指早期妊娠失敗，胎兒出生後死亡<ref name="Rob2014">{{Cite journal|title=Pregnancy loss|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/24047642|last=Robinson|first=Gail Erlick|date=2014-01|journal=Best Practice & Research. Clinical Obstetrics & Gynaecology|issue=1|doi=10.1016/j.bpobgyn.2013.08.012|volume=28|pages=169–178|issn=1532-1932|pmid=24047642|access-date=2020-12-24|archive-date=2021-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210224181951/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/24047642/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

<!-- Cause and diagnosis -->
導致死產的原因通常不明<ref name="NIH2014Def" />。可能的原因包含了如[[子癇前症|子癇前症]]等[[妊娠併發症|妊娠併發症]]，以及[[分娩#併發症與分娩風險|分娩期併發症]]如[[胎盤|胎盤]]或[[臍帶|臍帶]]的問題、[[出生缺陷|出生缺陷]]、[[瘧疾|瘧疾]]感染、母親健康狀況不佳<ref name="WHO2016" /><ref name="NIH2014Cau">{{cite web|title=What are possible causes of stillbirth?|url=https://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/stillbirth/topicinfo/Pages/causes.aspx|accessdate=4 October 2016|date=23 September 2014|publisher=NICHD|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161005123557/https://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/stillbirth/topicinfo/Pages/causes.aspx|archivedate=2016-10-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>。風險因子包含35歲以上產婦、吸菸、使用藥物、使用{{le|輔助生殖技術|Assisted reproductive technology}}以及第一次懷孕<ref name="NIH2014Risk">{{cite web|title=What are the risk factors for stillbirth?|url=https://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/stillbirth/topicinfo/Pages/risk.aspx|accessdate=4 October 2016|date=23 September 2014|publisher=NICHD|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161005132231/https://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/stillbirth/topicinfo/Pages/risk.aspx|archivedate=2016-10-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>。感覺沒有胎兒運動時可能被懷疑是死產。可通過[[超音波|超音波]]檢查而確認<ref name="NIH2014Diag">{{cite web|title=How is stillbirth diagnosed?|url=https://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/stillbirth/topicinfo/Pages/diagnosed.aspx|accessdate=4 October 2016|date=23 September 2014|publisher=NICHD|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161005131840/https://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/stillbirth/topicinfo/Pages/diagnosed.aspx|archivedate=5 October 2016|deadurl=no}}</ref>。

<!-- Treatment and prognosis -->
醫療系統改善可能可以預防全世界大多數死產<ref name="WHO2016" /><ref name="Lancet2016">{{cite journal|title=Ending preventable stillbirths An Executive Summary for The Lancet’s Series|url=http://www.thelancet.com/pb/assets/raw/Lancet/stories/series/stillbirths2016-exec-summ.pdf|date=Jan 2016|journal=The Lancet|accessdate=2017-08-26|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180712154237/http://www.thelancet.com/pb/assets/raw/Lancet/stories/series/stillbirths2016-exec-summ.pdf|archivedate=2018-07-12|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。大約五成的死產在[[分娩|分娩]]期間發生，且在[[發展中國家|發展中國家]]比[[已發展國家|已發展國家]]更常見<ref name="WHO2016" />。依照懷孕時間長短治療方式有所不同，懷孕早期可以使用藥物讓死胎排出，之後可使用{{le|擴張宮頸和清宮手術|dilation and evacuation}}處理<ref name="NIH2014Tx">{{cite web|title=How do health care providers manage stillbirth?|url=https://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/stillbirth/topicinfo/Pages/managed.aspx|publisher=NICHD|accessdate=4 October 2016|date=23 September 2014|archivedate=2016-10-05|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161005133645/https://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/stillbirth/topicinfo/Pages/managed.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。經歷死產後的女性有更高風險再次發生；然而大多數之後的懷孕並沒有相似的問題<ref>{{cite web|title=Stillbirth: Other FAQs|url=https://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/stillbirth/topicinfo/Pages/questions.aspx|publisher=NICHD|accessdate=4 October 2016|date=23 September 2014|archivedate=2016-10-05|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161005133552/https://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/stillbirth/topicinfo/Pages/questions.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[抑郁_(情绪)|抑鬱]]、{{le|經濟損失|Pure economic loss}}，和{{le|家庭破裂|Marital breakdown}}是已知的潛在影響<ref name="Lancet2016" />。

<!-- Epidemiology -->
2015年全球懷孕28週後約有260萬例死產（每45例出生約1例）<ref name="WHO2016" /><ref name="NIH2014Epi">{{cite web|title=How common is stillbirth?|url=https://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/stillbirth/topicinfo/Pages/how-common.aspx|accessdate=4 October 2016|date=23 September 2014|publisher=NICHD|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161005131327/https://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/stillbirth/topicinfo/Pages/how-common.aspx|archivedate=2016-10-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。最常見發生於發展中的國家，特別是[[南亞|南亞]]和[[撒哈拉以南非洲|撒哈拉以南非洲]]地區<ref name="WHO2016" />。以美國而言，每167個出生就有一個死胎。1950年以來，美國的死胎率下降了約2/3<ref name="NIH2014Epi" />。{{胎齡及胎兒發育}}

